Enum Class ServiceFactory

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ServiceFactory>
it.unicam.cs.mpgc.jbudget125576.infra.ServiceFactory
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ServiceFactory>, Constable
public enum ServiceFactory extends Enum<ServiceFactory>
Super-simple service factory providing lazily-created singletons.

This is intentionally tiny and fine for a JavaFX, mostly single-threaded app. Instances are created on first access and cached for the lifetime of the process. No synchronization is applied (by desing); if you need thread-safety, switch to DI.

Example


 // somewhere in a controller
 var catSvc = ServiceFactory.categories();
 var txSvc  = ServiceFactory.transactions();
 var dlSvc  = ServiceFactory.deadlines();
